messages.message: Hello! I'm trying to start a bunch of services in docker and they're all getting stuck in the same spot. Attached is a screenshot of what the redis logs look like (they all look basically the same). The containers are getting created but nothing is happening after that. Any ideas of why this may be happening?
I'm running `make build-docker run-docker` for all of these
It was a docker issue! For anyone seeing this, try clicking the bug icon in Docker desktop then using Clean / Purge data
